----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* General

 - All dialog less plugins which modify images should only use currentSelection().
 - All dialog less plugins which do not modify images should use either current* methods.
 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* SLIDESHOW PLUGIN 

 - Add preview Slideshow effects in dialogbox similar Kcontrol screensavers settings.
 - Auto-rotate according to EXIF orientation tag

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* MPEGENCODER PLUGIN

 - Add DIVX support using mencoder program.
 - Using new C++ implementation with MJPEGTools and IMLIB from Renchi instead images2mpg bash script.
 - Add file name or image comment in MPEG flux.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

* PRINTWIZARD PLUGIN

 - Check for existence of Gimp and disable option if not available.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* CALENDAR PLUGIN

 - Use QSimpleRichText to render the calendar text
 - Add more options for controlling the appearance.
 - Work on beautifying the calendar layout.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* SENDIMAGES PLUGIN

 - Add tarball, zip, bz2, gz generation.
 - Add support of 'Aethera' and 'Opera' mail agents.
